profile:
In our modern, hectic world, today's homeowners do not have the time or energy for the daily upkeep associated with most swimming pools. Durham Fiberglass Pools understands this and is proud to offer you high quality San Juan Fiberglass Pools, spas, and accessories. We provide a nearly maintenance-free centerpiece to the backyard resort you've always dreamed of, giving you more time with family and friends. With a state of the art fiberglass swimming pool you have the advantages of the lowest maintenance and upkeep of any pool in the industry, reduced operating costs, and the peace of mind that comes from having the best warranty in the industry.

Based in Durham Region, we service all of Southern Ontario including Toronto. We provide high-quality installation with the personal service that only a family-run business can offer.

At Durham Fiberglass Pools, we care about our customers.

profile:
Mark's Pools Plus Group provides full swimming pool, spa and fountain service and repair to help keep your residential or commercial system running smoothly. We recommend meeting you on-site for a no-charge, no-obligation analysis of your swimming pool equipment. We dispatch one of our full-time, year-round employees to complete the service. We offer single or multiple days per week service to match your needs. Call us for ongoing service, start-ups, one-time cleanings, pool inspections or whatever your pool needs might be. We service, renovate & install in ground pools. above ground pools, on ground pools, water falls and spa's. We are family owned and operated, licensed, and insured. Our employee's are Certified Pool Operators. We maintain our database and training yearly and follow The City of Toronto Public Health Department recommendations to ensure compliance for your health and safety. Meaning your pool will be up to date with any issues we may find that has been over looked by other pool companies and their technicians.
